  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape From V.I. is a 2D sidescrolling 1st Person Survival Horror game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>STORY:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After an abrupt catastrophe rocks your workplace, you must attempt to flee to the surface as quickly as possible. Unfortunately, a peculiar artifact transports the player to a new dimension halting their escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What was once a simple passage to freedom, quickly becomes a dimension-hopping game of survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encountering a plethora of horrifying monsters across multiple worlds, the player will discover, and face the truth about their own past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GAMEPLAY:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player only has 1 life with no checkpoints or autosaves (A save is made upon quitting to the main menu)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are branching paths within the game, meaning the choices the player makes, affect the ending they get.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whenever the player switches from 2D to 3D their position in the world is saved so they can navigate the world in unique ways.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape From V.I. is a 2D sidescrolling 1st Person Survival Horror game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>STORY:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After an abrupt catastrophe rocks your workplace, you must attempt to flee to the surface as quickly as possible. Unfortunately, a peculiar artifact transports the player to a new dimension halting their escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What was once a simple passage to freedom, quickly becomes a dimension-hopping game of survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encountering a plethora of horrifying monsters across multiple worlds, the player will discover, and face the truth about their own past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GAMEPLAY:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player only has 1 life with no checkpoints or autosaves (A save is made upon quitting to the main menu)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are branching paths within the game, meaning the choices the player makes, affect the ending they get.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whenever the player switches from 2D to 3D their position in the world is saved so they can navigate the world in unique ways.</p>",
